and rules continue to act freely,

1402
01:47:05,066 --> 01:47:06,366
and no one can stop them.

1403
01:47:06,733 --> 01:47:08,366
In such situations,

1404
01:47:10,900 --> 01:47:15,733
The prudent choice for everyone
is to let go of conflict

1405
01:47:15,766 --> 01:47:18,133
and move toward
cooperation.

1406
01:47:19,466 --> 01:47:20,866
And,

1407
01:47:24,266 --> 01:47:29,333
a development-driven approach is the
way forward, expansionism will not work.

1408
01:47:30,966 --> 01:47:36,033
As I’ve said before, the world is
interdependent and interconnected.

1409
01:47:36,033 --> 01:47:40,366
Every nation needs one another, no one can
stand alone.

1410
01:47:42,733 --> 01:47:47,733
And from all the different forums I
attend, one thing is clear,

1411
01:47:48,533 --> 01:47:51,366
everyone is deeply worried about these
conflicts.

1412
01:47:52,633 --> 01:47:55,533
We can only hope that peace is restored
very soon.

1413
01:47:57,800 --> 01:48:01,633
- I'm not very good at this.
- You keep looking at your watch.

1414
