you have seen a lot of difficult situation
in the history of India,

1418
01:48:19,133 --> 01:48:24,166
one of them, the 2002 Gujarat riots.

1419
01:48:24,533 --> 01:48:27,966
They are one of the most challenging
period of modern Indian history

1420
01:48:28,533 --> 01:48:32,533
when there was violence between Hindu and
