1421
01:48:33,166 --> 01:48:35,233
that led to over one thousand deaths.

1422
01:48:35,833 --> 01:48:40,733
It revealed the intensity of religious
tension in the region,

1423
01:48:41,033 --> 01:48:44,266
you were, as you mentioned, Chief Minister
of Gujarat at that time.

1424
01:48:44,833 --> 01:48:48,233
Looking back, what lessons do you draw
from that time?

1425
01:48:48,666 --> 01:48:53,233
And we should also say that India's
independent Supreme court upheld twice,

1426
01:48:53,633 --> 01:48:58,033
in twelve and twenty two they you had no
