1433
01:49:24,733 --> 01:49:30,566
You've done extensive research and have
dived deeply into every small detail.

1434
01:49:31,233 --> 01:49:36,733
So, I think you've done very well.

1435
01:49:36,966 --> 01:49:39,466
And all the efforts you've put in during
our conversation,

1436
01:49:39,466 --> 01:49:44,033
and in all your conversations, are
appreciated.

1437
01:49:44,566 --> 01:49:49,433
And rather than
simply interviewing me,

1438
01:49:50,433 --> 01:49:53,933
I feel you're trying to deeply understand
India.

1439
01:49:54,133 --> 01:49:57,633
That's why I strongly feel there's genuine
honesty

1440
01:49:57,766 --> 01:50:01,233
in your sincere effort
to uncover the truth.

1441
01:50:01,633 --> 01:50:05,333
And for that sincere approach, I genuinely
congratulate you.

1442
01:50:05,800 --> 01:50:07,800
- Thank you
- Regarding the

1443
01:50:08,000 --> 01:50:10,700
earlier events that you mentioned,

1444
01:50:12,033 --> 01:50:15,933
like the 2002 riots in Gujarat,

1445
01:50:17,133 --> 01:50:19,133
I'd like to paint you

1446
01:50:19,733 --> 01:50:26,466
a clearer picture of
the 12 to 15 months leading up to that,

1447
01:50:27,033 --> 01:50:32,933
so you can fully understand, uh, the
atmosphere of that time.

1448
01:50:33,066 --> 01:50:34,466
For instance,

1449
01:50:35,633 --> 01:50:39,300
take December 24, 1999,

1450
01:50:40,833 --> 01:50:42,733
roughly three years earlier:

1451
01:50:43,733 --> 01:50:47,033
An Indian flight from Kathmandu to Delhi
was hijacked,

1452
01:50:48,033 --> 01:50:51,466
