if I had to summarize in one sentence, I
welcome it.

1538
01:57:35,133 --> 01:57:37,066
I have a strong belief

1539
01:57:38,633 --> 01:57:43,633
that criticism is
the soul of democracy.

1540
01:57:44,466 --> 01:57:46,566
If democracy truly

1541
01:57:47,500 --> 01:57:51,833
runs in your veins, you
must embrace it.

1542
01:57:53,633 --> 01:57:59,333
In our scriptures, it’s said: "Always keep
your critics close."

1543
01:58:00,300 --> 01:58:05,133
Critics should be your nearest companions
because through genuine criticism,

1544
01:58:06,333 --> 01:58:11,433
you can improve quickly and work
democratically with better insights.

1545
01:58:13,300 --> 01:58:18,000
In fact, I believe we should have more
criticism,

1546
01:58:18,166 --> 01:58:22,233
and it should be sharp and well-informed.

1547
01:58:23,266 --> 01:58:29,233
But my real complaint is that nowadays,
what we see isn't real criticism.

1548
01:58:30,033 --> 01:58:34,133
Genuine criticism requires thorough study,

1549
01:58:34,166 --> 01:58:36,666
in-depth research, and careful analysis.

1550
01:58:36,800 --> 01:58:39,766
It demands finding the truth from
falsehoods.

1551
01:58:40,133 --> 01:58:43,366
Today, people look for shortcuts,

1552
01:58:43,533 --> 01:58:47,433
avoid proper research,
and skip deep analysis.

1553
01:58:47,933 --> 01:58:52,833
Instead of identifying genuine weaknesses,
they jump straight to accusations.

1554
01:58:54,666 --> 01:58:58,566
There's a big difference between
allegations and criticism.

1555
01:58:59,233 --> 01:59:04,366
The references you're giving, they are
allegations, not criticism.

1556
01:59:04,766 --> 01:59:08,133
For a strong democracy, genuine criticism
is necessary.

1557
01:59:08,733 --> 01:59:13,366
Allegations benefit no one; they just
cause unnecessary conflicts.

1558
01:59:14,233 --> 01:59:18,666
That's why I always welcome criticism
openly.

1559
01:59:18,900 --> 01:59:21,166
And whenever false accusations arise,

1560
01:59:21,233 --> 01:59:27,533
I calmly continue serving my country with
complete dedication.

1561
01:59:28,133 --> 01:59:30,933
- Yeah, the thing you speak of, is very
important to me

1562
01:59:30,966 --> 01:59:33,433
because I admire great journalism.

1563
01:59:34,433 --> 01:59:41,433
And unfortunately, in modern day, a lot of
journalists seek clickbait headlines,

1564
01:59:41,733 --> 01:59:45,233
