shot.

1566
01:59:49,633 --> 01:59:53,266
I think there is room and desire and
hunger for great journalists,

1567
01:59:53,333 --> 01:59:55,266
and that requires deep understanding.

1568
01:59:55,433 --> 01:59:59,566
And it saddens me how often one of the
reasons,

1569
01:59:59,633 --> 02:00:01,366
you know, I don't think I'm very good at
this,

1570
02:00:01,433 --> 02:00:05,266
but one of the reasons I really wanted to
